Usage: write_instance_obs [-help] <file> -layer <layer> [-with_outer_shape]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
<file>             # The name of output file (string, required)
-layer <layer>     # The layer of OBS to be written ((layer), required)
-with_outer_shape  # Default, command only save the OBS shape in inst boundary.
                   # If user saves OBS with this option, tool can save the OBS
                   # shape out of the inst boundary also. (bool, optional)